Patrick Shai has graced our TV screens for years on a list of popular shows such as Soul City, Generations and most recently, The River. JOHANNESBURG - Patrick Shai is being laid to rest on Saturday in Soweto. The legendary actor died last weekend. WATCH: Memorial service for actor Patrick Shai Shai has graced our TV screens for years on a list of popular shows such as Soul City, Generations and most recently, The River. As a reformed abuser, Shai used his past experiences to fight against gender-based violence, through his work as the ambassador of Brothers for Life and his foundation, Khuluma Ndoda.